bour.camus.gameofgooses.ui

Interface IGameWatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConsoleUI

    public interface IGameWatcher
    IGameWatcher allows a class to receive informations about the run of a game. Each method is called upon certain events. By implementing this interface, you can create your own interface for the game.
    Author:
    Armand BOUR
